title: SBI to add 600 branches in its network during FY25: Chairman Setty
description: SBI plans to open 600 branches this financial year, targeting emerging areas and large residential townships. The bank aims to improve customer reach and offers innovative products like a combo of recurring deposits and SIP. SBI also focuses on deposit mobilization through extensive outreach programs. SBI has a network of over 22,500 branches across India.
